Features projected for 0.0.3:
  - add a close button to channels in Circe
  - redirect debug messages to the special debug window. This window can be reached as any channel window  via the name "debug".
Features projected for the future:
  - add private messaging support to Circe (requires an addition to window_base.py)
  - add plugins (requires a change of wxserver.py)

- PERHAPS redirect debug messages in the special debug window. This window can be
  reached as any channel window via the name "debug".

- (wxserver.py) In self.checkEvents() in WXServer add handling for missing
  events.
